      "title": "Broken Bow Memorial Stadium",
      "score": 0.04117095533209397,
      "text": "Broken Bow Memorial Stadium\nHistoric Broken Bow Memorial Stadium has served as the home of the Broken Bow Savages, since it was constructed in 1936 by the National Youth Administration, a part of the Works Progress Administration.",
